  "description": [
    "Page 2 SAYS FRANCO SHOULD NOT BE ALLOWED AT PEACE TABLE By CHATWOOD HALL Only Negro correspondent in Russia MOSCOW Nov 28 ANP Franco Spains gory axeman swears he is no fascist He has de clared Spain a neutral in this war and now demands a seat at the com ing peace conference Just what could Franco have to talk about over a peace table He could relate how he called in and welcomed Fascist German war planes to rehearse World War II by the bombing of Madrid and Guern ica and permitted Fascist Italian tanks to be used against his coun trymen he could also tell how he adopted the Nazi German salute for his army and permitted Italian war ship to use the Balearic islands as a base from which to carry on piracy against both the Spanish Republi can and British shipping carrying goods to the Republicans Franco might discuss at the peace table how he used neutral Spain in the present war as a corridor through which needed supplies and raw material flowed to Fascist Ger many and is now using Spanish neu trality as an escape route for big shot Nazis to go to Argentina"
  ],
